  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>tortillas</strong> to&nbsp;a large baking tray</p>\r\n<p>Place the baking tray in the oven and cook for 4-5 min or until the tortillas are starting to turn brown around the edges</p>\r\n<p>Once browned, remove the <strong>tortillas</strong> from the oven and set them aside</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>\r\n<p>Strip the <strong>basil leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop the <strong>stalks</strong> finely, leaving the <strong>leaves</strong> whole for later</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>tomato paste</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a heat-proof bowl</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>garlic, chopped basil stalks, </strong>1 tsp<strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> sugar</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>to the bowl &ndash; this is your<strong> tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, tear the&nbsp;<strong>mozzarella</strong>&nbsp;into large pieces</p>\r\n<p>Pat the torn <strong>mozzarella</strong>&nbsp;with kitchen paper, pressing down very firmly so that the mozzarella is nice and dry (this stops your pizzas from being soggy)</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>baby&nbsp;plum tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> between the&nbsp;<strong>tortillas</strong> and spread it out towards the edges&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Top with the <strong>torn</strong>&nbsp;<strong>mozzarella</strong>, <strong>basil leaves</strong> and <strong>halved baby plum tomatoes</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and return to the oven for a further 8-10 min or until the <strong>mozzarella</strong> has fully melted and the <strong>tortillas</strong> are crispy &ndash; these&nbsp;are your <strong>tortizzas</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong>&nbsp;finely with a peeler, until you end up with a pile of<strong> cheese shavings</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>wild</strong>&nbsp;<strong>rocket&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once the <strong>tort<strong>izzas</strong> </strong>are done,&nbsp;top each one with a handful of the&nbsp;<strong>rocket</strong> and a drizzle of<strong>&nbsp;olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Garnish with the <strong>cheese shavings&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/975_-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>tort</strong><strong>izzas</strong> into quarters and serve</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
